      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get why you say that but i've been feeling this way for like three weeks now and it's not like a sudden thing. it just feels more like i'm losing my stamina. my friend said it's probably just because i'm in my 50s now and things slow down. do you think it could really just be age causing it? i really dont want to deal with a hospital visit if it's just aging.",
